	>
	</div>
	<span
		class="text-xs inline-block text-muted py-2 px-3 border border-emerald-500/80 rounded-2xl animate-shimmer items-center justify-center bg-[linear-gradient(110deg,#1ddf2d03,45%,#10d49349,55%,#1ddf2d03)] bg-[length:200%_100%] transition-colors"
		>Disponible para trabajar</span
	>
